Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.05,0:00:29.68,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}吹乾流下的淚珠輕拂而去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.76,0:00:39.66,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}不管是誰 對未來都有著一股不安的期望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.70,0:00:48.04,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}就朝著明天大步邁進吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.18,0:00:51.35,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}GUNPARADE MARCH
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.35,0:00:57.75,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}總有一天會覺醒的 真實之心扉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.89,0:01:04.02,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}現在就伸出雙手去感受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.06,0:01:12.66,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}在這開始變化的世界 立刻前往探尋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.70,0:01:20.30,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}牽繫著你的手絕不再分離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.84,0:01:22.97,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}因為有你在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.21,0:01:27.84,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\fs20\fad(100,100)}所以一定找尋的到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.63,0:01:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原學姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.63,0:01:46.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我覺得這樣還是不好啦 更何況我們還有穿著規定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.10,0:01:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果被軍方的人臨檢到的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.47,0:01:52.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你放心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.07,0:01:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會有事的 我調查過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.71,0:01:57.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.05,0:02:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,何況我們連暑假都沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.08,0:02:03.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,偶爾找點樂趣無所謂的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.85,0:02:06.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是只有我們這樣的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.36,0:02:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒關係 因為我們選對工作啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.96,0:02:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想喝茶就由我們請客吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.46,0:02:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兩位小姐在這個時間兜風嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.53,0:02:18.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.27,0:02:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們要去哪裏呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.50,0:02:22.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要去熊本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.07,0:02:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還蠻遠的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.84,0:02:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,學姊 我們快走啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.14,0:02:29.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才一下下 沒關係的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.04,0:02:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不介意的話 我們送你們過去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.28,0:02:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就這麼決定吧 很快就會到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.35,0:02:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們的車子有這麼快嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.06,0:02:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要說快當然快咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.52,0:02:46.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我們是用汽油車 汽油車喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.87,0:02:55.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,V8的汽車 你竟然還留著啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.37,0:02:59.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是瞭解 難道你喜歡車嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.57,0:03:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該說是喜歡機器類的東西吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.21,0:03:06.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那時候的設計真是棒呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.12,0:03:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,流線造型實在是好漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.32,0:03:11.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒、沒錯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.75,0:03:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然能開這種車 真是有錢呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.89,0:03:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這也沒什麼啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.92,0:03:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還不錯呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.49,0:03:20.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就趕快出發吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.03,0:03:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯 趕快出發\N你們的車就由我開吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.43,0:03:29.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣不太好意思啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.60,0:03:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用介意這種事惰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.07,0:03:35.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過我們的車有一點點大喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.28,0:03:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒問題的 是哪一台？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.91,0:03:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那一台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.66,0:03:51.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,學姊 時間差不多咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.96,0:03:53.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再見咯 少爺們～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.27,0:04:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那種的不可能會開吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.31,0:04:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,「第四話  雙人搭檔」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.44,0:04:38.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,AMTT519W
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.07,0:04:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芝村重工業所開發的傑出泛用兵器「士魂」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.08,0:04:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,予以大幅改良後完成的新機種
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.22,0:04:51.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雙人座機構造使得武器與操縱系統分別獨立開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.32,0:04:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不只減少駕駛員的負擔 也大幅提升機動力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.59,0:05:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,內建之第六代人工肌肉 提供了壓倒性之瞬間爆發力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.33,0:05:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,外殼可反彈任何幻獸之攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.24,0:05:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加上以消滅所有敵人為前提之超強火力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.34,0:05:15.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,「士魂」雙人座機將實現您的夢想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.75,0:05:19.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,趁現在 瀧川
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.55,0:05:23.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看我的燃燒彈！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.62,0:05:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了 隆之！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.06,0:05:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,舞！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.70,0:05:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雙人座機真令人熱血沸騰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.87,0:05:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼…你要簽哪一支？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.37,0:05:43.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要挑幾組都可以喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.21,0:05:47.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每種組合都不太實際耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.81,0:05:49.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是這樣才有趣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.88,0:05:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好啦 再偷懶下去是會做不完的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.21,0:05:57.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經做完咯 新型果然比較好保養呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.52,0:05:59.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你只是來礙手礙腳的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.65,0:06:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,田邊這邊如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.52,0:06:02.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬上就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.52,0:06:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然做完的話 就來幫忙輸入資料吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.10,0:06:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.16,0:06:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過好像一直沒辦法敲定呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.30,0:06:13.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敲定是指駕駛員的挑選嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.10,0:06:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像是老師跟班長的意見不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.17,0:06:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會由誰來擔任呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.91,0:06:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由於還要進行模擬戰 所以快一點會比較好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.34,0:06:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那學姊要不要也來下注？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.85,0:06:27.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們又在玩這個啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.32,0:06:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,猜中的可以享用─個月的豪華點心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.32,0:06:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,田邊只選一組呢 真執著啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.33,0:06:39.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次我很有把握
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.56,0:06:41.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就先不要選這組…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.56,0:06:42.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.70,0:06:43.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這算是基本原則吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.44,0:06:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瀧川是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.87,0:06:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是看在他的熱血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.44,0:06:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過問題是不夠冷靜…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.21,0:06:58.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,壬生屋呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.28,0:07:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先不考慮吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.22,0:07:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.58,0:07:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,關於瀨戶口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.72,0:07:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然成績跟往常一樣 不過這次倒是幹勁十足
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.89,0:07:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過也只有幹勁是嗎\N{\fs20\fnsimhei}(希望小舞跟我搭檔)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.86,0:07:12.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.73,0:07:15.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芝村在成績上算是頂尖的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.60,0:07:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也很久沒看到這種成績了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.47,0:07:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過她並不適合跟他人合作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.30,0:07:24.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,速水的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.47,0:07:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的是相當普通的水準呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.24,0:07:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過這也算是他的優點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.25,0:07:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是棘手啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.98,0:07:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是要參考司令部的資料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.75,0:07:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓瀧川跟速水搭檔吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.69,0:07:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說得也是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.90,0:07:49.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣你覺得如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.27,0:07:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這實在是有點…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.34,0:07:56.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 就這樣決定吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.28,0:08:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,HWT雙人座機的駕駛員已經決定是這兩位了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.02,0:08:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是黑馬啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.52,0:08:15.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒被選上的也不要太在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.22,0:08:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,另外被選上的兩位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.23,0:08:21.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從明天起請更加專心練習
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.96,0:08:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起加油吧 芝村同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.35,0:08:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看過這種的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.35,0:08:42.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還是第一次看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.72,0:08:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,據說雙人座機的存活率比較高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.29,0:08:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該是因為有兩個人在駕駛吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.03,0:08:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你覺得呢 芝村同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.11,0:09:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼現在開始進行…\N{\fs20\fnsimhei}(我再也不信神了)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.44,0:09:13.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,HWT雙人座機的模擬訓練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.05,0:09:17.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實應該是我跟小舞的\N{\fs20\fnsimhei}假想敵將會以亂數設定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.49,0:09:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請兩位因應狀況做出行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.69,0:09:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好想發射飛彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.26,0:09:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,準備好了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.39,0:09:23.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.39,0:09:24.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,主系統啟動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.33,0:09:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,索敵雷達跟炮火管制系統正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.23,0:09:32.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,資料連結確認無誤 模擬戰鬥系統啟動
